public class PredicateProperty<T> extends javafx.beans.property.SimpleObjectProperty<Predicate<T>> implements Predicate<T>
This class implements property that wraps Predicate instance.

Default value is x -> true i.e. test(Object) will return true until the predicate is altered via set(Predicate).
